lastCommitMessage: refactor: enhance shipping option selection logic and improve code readability
- Updated the shipping option selection logic to prioritize available default options, followed by available options, and added fallback handling.
- Improved logging for better clarity on selected shipping options and fallback scenarios.
- Refactored related methods across multiple files to ensure consistency in shipping option handling.
These changes aim to enhance the user experience during checkout by ensuring optimal shipping options are selected.
